2001-12-21 21:13  gregor

	* jit2h.pl, Parrot/Jit/i386-bsd.pm, Parrot/Jit/i386-linux.pm,
	Parrot/Jit/i386-nojit.pm, lib/Parrot/Jit/i386-bsd.pm,
