2001-12-20 01:57  gregor

	* Configure.pl, MANIFEST, Makefile.in, interpreter.c, jit.c,
	jit2h.pl, test_main.c, Parrot/.cvsignore, Parrot/Jit/i386-bsd.pm,
	Parrot/Jit/i386-linux.pm, Parrot/Jit/i386-nojit.pm, docs/jit.pod,
